      <title>经济和战争担忧加剧，股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/stocks-set-for-losses-as-economy-war-fears-deepen-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对经济进一步放缓的担忧令交易员感到不安，同时他们还准备应对中东紧张局势加剧带来的更多波动，因此亚洲股市周一将出现下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/stocks-set-for-losses-as-economy-war-fears-deepen-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 22:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周全球大宗商品市场值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[被视为全球工业健康状况风向标的重型机械制造商卡特彼勒公司本周公布了第二季度业绩。中国正在加大小麦采购量，而铜投资者正在分析基金经理对这一关键工业金属前景的预测信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
