    <item>
      <title>据路透社报道，士力架制造商玛氏正在考虑收购凯拉诺瓦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/snickers-maker-mars-explores-buying-kellanova-k-reuters-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社报道，糖果巨头玛氏公司（Snickers and M&amp;M’s 等著名糖果的制造商）正在考虑收购凯拉诺瓦，这将成为包装食品行业有史以来最大的交易之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/snickers-maker-mars-explores-buying-kellanova-k-reuters-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:57:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯提高对亚洲石油价格，表明对需求有信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/saudi-arabia-hikes-oil-prices-to-asia-in-sign-of-faith-in-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯三个月来首次上调了对亚洲出口的旗舰原油价格，这一初步迹象表明，沙特阿拉伯对全球最大进口国亚洲的需求仍有信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/saudi-arabia-hikes-oil-prices-to-asia-in-sign-of-faith-in-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:50:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员大举押注美联储启动救援模式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bond-traders-bet-big-on-the-fed-launching-into-rescue-mode</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员纷纷押注美国经济即将迅速恶化，美联储将需要开始大幅放松货币政策，以避免经济衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bond-traders-bet-big-on-the-fed-launching-into-rescue-mode</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行维持鹰派立场，宽松周期落后于全球同行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/rba-set-for-hawkish-hold-trailing-global-peers-in-easing-cycle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚有望继续处于全球宽松周期的尾声，因为当地通胀和经济降温仍在加剧，这要求储备银行维持其基准利率在 12 年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/rba-set-for-hawkish-hold-trailing-global-peers-in-easing-cycle</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛经济学家将美国经济衰退风险“有限”上调至 25%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/goldman-economists-lift-limited-us-recession-risk-to-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团经济学家将未来一年美国经济衰退的可能性从 15% 提高到 25%，但他表示，即使失业率上升，也有几个理由不必担心经济衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/goldman-economists-lift-limited-us-recession-risk-to-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 17:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴菲特减持苹果股票 敦促投资者保持冷静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/apple-aapl-investors-urged-to-stay-calm-after-buffett-slashes-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有些人认为，伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 减持苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 股份可能被解读为对这家 iPhone 制造商的增长前景缺乏信心。但华尔街的许多人都敦促投资者不要太在意这些消息，保持冷静。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/apple-aapl-investors-urged-to-stay-calm-after-buffett-slashes-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:34:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
